      <title>中国考虑将高频交易费用提高十倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/china-weighs-tenfold-fee-increase-on-high-frequency-traders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国正考虑将高频交易的费用提高至少十倍，这是其为控制一些量化策略而做出的最新尝试，监管机构认为这些策略对国内以散户投资者为主导的股市的公平性构成了威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/china-weighs-tenfold-fee-increase-on-high-frequency-traders</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 07:00:42 GMT</pubDate>
